r the course of the project.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Before development starts, milestones for deliverables should be defined and a feedback cadence should be agreed upon. During development we think it is important to be transparent with the progress and raise potential issues as soon as possible. After commissioning, a support plan may be defined to ensure the system is maintained and continues to provide value over time.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->', 'Astemes', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '16-revision-v1', '', '', '2022-01-05 20:51:09', '2022-01-05 19:51:09', '', 16, 'http://31.217.196.224/~jaxedsws/legacy/?p=262', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(265, 1, '2022-01-11 14:55:27', '2022-01-11 13:55:27', '.wpforms-submit{\n	color: black !important;\n	background-color: white !important /*fix for strange bug*/\n}\n\n.widget-area{\n	margin-top: 0*var(--global--spacing-vertical);\n	grid-template-columns: none\n}\n\n:root{\n	/* Colors */\n	--global--color-black: #212121;\n	--global--color-dark-gray: #455a64;\n	--global--color-gray: #757575;\n	--global--color-light-gray: #CFD8DC;\n}\n\n.site-info{\n	margin-top:0*var(--global--spacing-vertical);\n	float: left\n}\n\n.site-footer > .site-info{\n	border-top: 0px\n}\n\n.site-name {\n}\n\n.footer-navigation{\n	margin-top: calc(1 * var(--global--spacing-vertical));\n	float: right\n}\n\n.site-main{\n	padding-bottom: 0\n}\n\n.powered-by{\n	visibility: hidden\n}', 'twentytwentyone', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '160-revision-v1', '', '', '2022-01-11 14:55:27', '2022-01-11 13:55:27', '', 160, 'http://31.217.196.224/~jaxedsws/legacy/?p=265', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
