(248, 1, '2021-12-07 11:53:58', '2021-12-07 10:53:58', '<!-- wp:columns {\"align\":\"wide\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns alignwide\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Get in touch with us to get more information about our services and to learn how we may help you solve your test and measurement challenges. Give us a call or use the form below to get in touch.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"className\":\"is-style-default\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-style-default\"><!-- wp:columns {\"className\":\"is-style-default\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-style-default\"><!-- wp:column {\"width\":\"170px\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\" style=\"flex-basis:170px\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":246,\"sizeSlug\":\"thumbnail\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\",\"className\":\"is-style-rounded\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-thumbnail is-style-rounded\"><img src=\"http://www.astemes.com/staging/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Sundqvist_Anton-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"Anton Sundqvist\" class=\"wp-image-246\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column {\"width\":\"\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"typography\":{\"lineHeight\":\"1.5\"}}} -->\n<p style=\"line-height:1.5\">Anton Sundqvist<br><a href=\"tel:+358447272425\">+358 (0) 44 727 2425<br></a><a href=\"mailto:anton.sundqvist@astemes.com\">anton.sundqvist@astemes.com<br></a><a href=\"https://linkedin.com/anton-sundqvist\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">https://linkedin.com/anton-sundqvist</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Contact', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '151-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-12-07 11:53:58', '2021-12-07 10:53:58', '', 151, 'http://www.astemes.com/staging/?p=248', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(249, 1, '2021-12-07 17:48:20', '2021-12-07 16:48:20', '<!-- wp:heading {\"className\":\"alignwide has-text-align-wide\",\"style\":{\"typography\":{\"lineHeight\":\"1.1\",\"fontSize\":\"90px\"}}} -->\n<h2 class=\"alignwide has-text-align-wide\" style=\"font-size:90px;line-height:1.1\">Test and Measurement Solutions<p class=\"has-text-align-wide\"></p></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns {\"align\":\"wide\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns alignwide\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Astemes is a solutions provider for test and measurement applications. We develop systems to automate testing of electro-mechanical products through the entire product life cycle. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We are your partner in test automation. From early proof-of-concepts and prototyping, through validation and verification, production testing, and beyond. We have high certified competency in the NI LabVIEW and NI TestStand software as well as extensive experience using and integrating various measurement devices and instruments. We are also highly effective working in Python and comfortable with C++ and Java.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Software Development</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We build high quality software for test and measurement applications. We provide software development services based on your needs, working either as part of your team or independently. Because communication is at least as important as problem solving in software engineering, we prefer to work incrementally where we continuously deliver business value and gather feedback.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Turn-Key Solutions</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The best results are achieved when we get involved early on during requirement gathering and design specification. After this phase we lead the project and find the best components and subcontractors, to deliver according to the agreed upon schedule. We work hard to keep the customer involved through the whole project to validate our understanding and steer the project along the way.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Training</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We offer tailored training, presentations and workshops related to testing, process and software development. We either schedule the sessions over a shorter time period or define a cadence with sessions spread out over a longer period. The content may be delivered either on-site, remotely, or as a combination of the two. We also offer professional code reviews and pair programming.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>How We Work</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We use industry standard technologies and proven frameworks to efficiently produce high quality software. By leveraging open source and proprietary software for common and generic tasks, we can focus on the core domain problems and avoid reinventing known solutions. This also reduces the maintenance cost and total cost of ownership over the lifecycle of the system.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Our project model starts with a defining phase where the needs and requirements are assessed. This phase may include a pre-study to clarify the requirements. The outcome of this first phase should be a verified understanding of the needs and a proposal for a solution. In many cases the actual requirements are not known at this stage and they will evolve over the course of the project.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Before the actual development starts, milestones for deliverables should be defined and a feedback cadence should be agreed upon. During development we think it is important to be transparent with the progress and raise potential issues as soon as possible. The source code of the software is always provided as part of the delivery. After commissioning, a support plan may be defined to ensure the system is maintained and continues to provide value over time.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->', 'Astemes', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '16-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-12-07 17:48:20', '2021-12-07 16:48:20', '', 16, 'http://www.astemes.com/staging/?p=249', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(250, 1, '2021-12-07 18:06:11', '2021-12-07 17:06:11', '<!-- wp:columns {\"align\":\"wide\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns alignwide\"><!-- wp:column {\"width\":\"100%\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\" style=\"flex-basis:100%\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>An automated test system is software and hardware tightly integrated to make a set of measurements which are evaluated to provide a test result. In some cases, the test result may be a dataset which is further analyzed by a domain expert, and in other cases a result may be a functional pass/fail result.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Some systems are used for repetitive measurements of the same type and others may need to be highly configurable to allow for reusing the same hardware for many types of tests. The types and number of inputs and outputs in the system will be highly dependent on the product under test and the purpose of the test. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>To build a successful test system the hardware must be suitable for the task and the software needs to be of the right quality. When we talk about software quality, we value two aspects above other. First, the software should behave as expected. And second, it should be easy to change. This is simply another way of saying that the system should do what it is supposed to do and have a good design.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Our software and hardware platform are very flexible and allows for any measurement, instrument, communication bus or protocol. Building software on our flexible framework, the development is accelerated and delivered with minimal technical risk. Using a proven software architecture, the cost of updating and maintaining the system is also greatly reduced.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns {\"align\":\"wide\",\"textColor\":\"black\",\"style\":{\"color\":{\"background\":\"#cfd8dc\"}}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns alignwide has-black-color has-text-color has-background\" style=\"background-color:#cfd8dc\"><!-- wp:column {\"verticalAlignment\":\"top\",\"width\":\"50%\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-top\" style=\"flex-basis:50%\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Development Test</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":166,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img src=\"http://www.astemes.com/staging/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/DevelopmentTest.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-166\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>When developing a product, a massive amount of data is required to make decisions on the design and construction. By automating repetitive tests, more time can be spent innovating. Test results are easier to analyze and compare if the data is acquired by an automated system and tedious report writing can further be automated. A good test system for product development is flexible and configurable by the user, who is typically a domain expert and may not be a programmer. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Production Test</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":169,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img src=\"http://www.astemes.com/staging/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Production-Test-3.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-169\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>When manufacturing a product, testing is often essential to ensure that the product functions as expected and has no defects. A good test system can reduce the time spent on testing, while proving the quality of the product through measurements. By collecting highly structured data, trends in production may be identified and supply chain issues may be identified early. A good test system for production is reliable, but it should also be ridiculously easy to use with minimal training.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns {\"verticalAlignment\":\"top\",\"align\":\"wide\",\"textColor\":\"black\",\"style\":{\"color\":{\"background\":\"#cfd8dc\"}}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns alignwide are-vertically-aligned-top has-black-color has-text-color has-background\" style=\"background-color:#cfd8dc\"><!-- wp:column {\"verticalAlignment\":\"top\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-top\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Embedded Software Test</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":167,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img src=\"http://www.astemes.com/staging/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Embedded-Test-1.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-167\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>When testing embedded software, it is desirable to run the software on real hardware with actual physical signals. It is common to model the environment and it is desirable to test possible edge cases and fault modes. In order to accurately simulate the real world with realistic timing, the test software and simulation models often needs to run in hard real time. This is usually referred to as hardware-in-the-loop (HIL) testing. The test system may be linked to a CI system to automatically run regression tests for each new build.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column {\"verticalAlignment\":\"top\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-top\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Monitoring &amp; Life-Time Test</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":168,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img src=\"http://www.astemes.com/staging/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Monitoring.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-168\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>A monitoring system gathers data on a product while in use, either in the field or in a controlled environment. Condition monitoring is often applied to high value assets for predictive maintenance and fault detection. A good monitoring system is reliable even when deployed in an uncertain environment. It is often desirable to do triggering on special events and to perform analysis at the edge to reduce the amount of raw data to be stored.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns {\"align\":\"wide\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns alignwide\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Astemes provide services tailored to your needs and priorities, from supporting your development team to delivering complete turnkey systems. By using iterative development practices, large upfront requirement specification may be avoided. Incremental deliveries, using prototypes and mock-ups, greatly reduces both technical risk and misunderstandings. Each delivery adds value as new knowledge is obtained and allows for regular course corrections. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If you have challenges like the ones described above, we want to learn more about your situation and have a discussion on how we could help you achieve your goals. Engage with us using the contact form below or by giving us a call.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->', 'Test Systems', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '84-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-12-07 18:06:11', '2021-12-07 17:06:11', '', 84, 'http://www.astemes.com/staging/?p=250', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(251, 1, '2021-12-07 19:08:25', '2021-12-07 18:08:25', '<!-- wp:heading {\"className\":\"alignwide has-text-align-wide\",\"style\":{\"typography\":{\"lineHeight\":\"1.1\",\"fontSize\":\"90px\"}}} -->\n<h2 class=\"alignwide has-text-align-wide\" style=\"font-size:90px;line-height:1.1\">Test and Measurement Solutions<p class=\"has-text-align-wide\"></p></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns {\"align\":\"wide\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns alignwide\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Astemes is a solutions provider for test and measurement applications. We develop systems to automate testing of electro-mechanical products through the entire product life cycle. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We are your partner in test automation. From early proof-of-concepts and prototyping, through validation and verification, production testing, and beyond. We have high certified competency in the NI LabVIEW and NI TestStand software as well as extensive experience using and integrating various measurement devices and instruments. We are also highly effective working in Python and comfortable with C++ and Java.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Software Development</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We build high quality software for test and measurement applications. We provide software development services based on your needs, working either as part of your team or independently. Because communication is at least as important as problem solving in software engineering, we prefer to work incrementally where we continuously deliver business value and gather feedback.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Turn-Key Solutions</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The best results are achieved when we get involved early on during requirement gathering and design specification. After this phase we lead the project and find the best components and subcontractors, to deliver according to the agreed upon schedule. We work hard to keep the customer involved through the whole project to validate our understanding and steer the project along the way.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Training</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We offer tailored training, presentations and workshops related to testing, process and software development. We either schedule the sessions over a shorter time period or define a cadence with sessions spread out over a longer period. The content may be delivered either on-site, remotely, or as a combination of the two. We also offer professional code reviews and pair programming.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>How We Work</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We use industry standard technologies and proven frameworks to efficiently produce high quality software. By leveraging open source and proprietary software for common and generic tasks, we can focus on the core domain problems and avoid reinventing known solutions. This also reduces the maintenance cost and total cost of ownership over the lifecycle of the system.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Our project model starts with a defining phase where the needs and requirements are assessed. This phase may include a pre-study to clarify the requirements. The outcome of this first phase should be a verified understanding of the needs and a proposal for a solution. In many cases the actual requirements are not known at this stage and they will evolve over the course of the project.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Before development starts, milestones for deliverables should be defined and a feedback cadence should be agreed upon. During development we think it is important to be transparent with the progress and raise potential issues as soon as possible. After commissioning, a support plan may be defined to ensure the system is maintained and continues to provide value over time.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->', 'Astemes', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '16-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-12-07 19:08:25', '2021-12-07 18:08:25', '', 16, 'http://www.astemes.com/staging/?p=251', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(252, 1, '2021-12-07 19:17:20', '2021-12-07 18:17:20', '<!-- wp:columns {\"align\":\"wide\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns alignwide\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Astemes provides expertise in design and development of automated test and measurement systems. Our mission is to enable innovation and excellence by providing world class technical expertise. We value software craftmanship and continuously work to improve and widen our offerings by actively participating in the international community. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We have high certified competency within the NI toolchain, including the <strong>Certified LabVIEW Architect (CLA)</strong> and <strong>Certified TestStand Developer (CTD)</strong> certifications. The CLA is the highest level of certification offered for <strong>NI LabVIEW</strong>. We are also highly effective working in <strong>Python </strong>and comfortable with <strong>Java </strong>and <strong>C++</strong>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We value transparency and always deliver to the best of our ability. While we do want our customers to come back, we have no intention to lock you in. Source code and documentation is, for this reason, always provided as part of our deliveries.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Astemes is based in Pietarsaari, Finland.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:gallery {\"ids\":[164,165],\"linkTo\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-2 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img src=\"http://www.astemes.com/staging/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/CLA_2.png\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"164\" data-full-url=\"http://www.astemes.com/staging/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/CLA_2.png\" data-link=\"http://www.astemes.com/staging/cla_2/\" class=\"wp-image-164\"/></figure></li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img src=\"http://www.astemes.com/staging/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/CTD.png\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"165\" data-full-url=\"http://www.astemes.com/staging/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/CTD.png\" data-link=\"http://www.astemes.com/staging/ctd/\" class=\"wp-image-165\"/></figure></li></ul></figure>\n<!-- /wp:gallery -->', 'About us', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '150-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-12-07 19:17:20', '2021-12-07 18:17:20', '', 150, 'http://www.astemes.com/staging/?p=252', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
